title: Oversized Moses Co-ord Set
description:
Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit Our Men's collection presents the perfect blend of
style and comfort with our Mauve Colour Co-ord Sets. Crafted for the summer season, these regular
fit ensembles offer a relaxed yet fashionable look. This Mauve Colour adds a touch of elegance to
any outfit, while the co-ord design ensures a cohesive and trendy appearance. Ideal for everyday
wear, these sets are versatile and effortlessly enhance your summer wardrobe. Embrace the season
with our refreshing Blush Colour Co-ord Sets and make a fashion statement wherever you go. - Wash
Care: Machine wash, Do not bleach - Fit Type: Relaxed Fit - Fabric: 67% Cotton, 31% Polyester, 2%
Elastane - Men's Monotone Co-ords set for everyday casual wear with two side pockets
